  "texts": [
    "After searching by selected search query were obtained 37 articles from 2019 to 2023.",
    "Because the same search query was performed in three different databases, in the screening step, was removed duplicated studies (11 studies removed) and records were verified by inclusion/exclusion criteria (4 studies excluded).",
    "A deeper analysis of the found articles allowed us to notice that some articles we knew about weren't included in the search results.",
    "That way, we used snowball sampling and added several scientific articles (4 studies), which included the mentioned terms and the main scientific question.",
    "An interim analysis of the keyword map from 9 articles indicated the need to apply a relevancy analysis of full-text articles (eligibility step)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}